      "content": "it's just that even the help feels fake. i'm sitting here trying to explain this to you, and i'm already thinking about how i'll describe this conversation to someone else later just so it sounds 'meaningful' enough for them. it's like i can't even exist without a witness. if the person who is supposed to be living this life isn't even there... wouldn't it just be easier to stop the noise?",
